WEBVTT

00:15.460 --> 00:19.960
♪During the dark night♪

00:20.100 --> 00:22.750
♪A guiding light♪

00:23.260 --> 00:25.050
♪Just like you♪

00:25.460 --> 00:29.750
♪Makes life turn bright♪

00:30.330 --> 00:35.180
♪Breaking free from darkness♪

00:35.400 --> 00:38.880
♪You gave me strength♪

00:39.230 --> 00:41.780
♪Running for truth♪

00:41.800 --> 00:45.850
♪I find my path♪

00:46.600 --> 00:50.580
♪Drawing on the hope♪

00:51.200 --> 00:54.580
♪That you render me♪

00:55.130 --> 00:58.010
♪In this long journey♪

00:58.260 --> 01:01.680
♪I run on lightly♪

01:19.180 --> 01:22.980
[Reborn]
[Adapted from Qiang Yu's work, Reborn]

01:23.220 --> 01:24.610
53.2 yuan.

01:27.100 --> 01:28.850
78.7 yuan.

01:31.220 --> 01:32.780
79.5 yuan.

01:34.780 --> 01:35.650
How much is the total?

01:35.979 --> 01:36.780
Is that all?

01:36.860 --> 01:37.650
That's all.

01:38.060 --> 01:40.420
Since the fast food restaurant
at the intersection opened,

01:40.810 --> 01:43.620
our revenue in the past few days
has been reduced by half.

01:43.979 --> 01:46.490
I heard that their rice and meat

01:46.490 --> 01:47.460
are all pre-frozen.

01:47.460 --> 01:49.580
They just put it in a microwave oven,

01:49.580 --> 01:50.420
and someone will eat it?

01:53.259 --> 01:54.050
I don't get it.

01:55.009 --> 01:56.259
They're making a lot of money

01:56.300 --> 01:57.620
delivering food to university students.

01:57.820 --> 02:00.300
How about we print more fliers tomorrow?

02:00.580 --> 02:02.220
Let's hand out fliers

02:02.860 --> 02:03.860
to surrounding schools
and residential buildings.

02:04.450 --> 02:05.260
Sure.

02:06.050 --> 02:07.620
We're just going to suffer
for these two years.

02:07.900 --> 02:10.009
Once we clear our debt

02:10.500 --> 02:11.820
and Qingyu graduates from university,

02:12.220 --> 02:13.180
things will get better.

02:15.650 --> 02:16.940
Other parents bring fruits,
delicious food,

02:16.940 --> 02:18.860
or nutritional supplements

02:18.860 --> 02:19.980
after work,

02:21.620 --> 02:23.130
while we bring vegetable leaves
for our children

02:23.329 --> 02:24.410
every time.

02:24.690 --> 02:26.620
Didn't I eat it all?

02:30.380 --> 02:32.290
I went to Jinyu's parents' meeting
this afternoon.

02:32.570 --> 02:32.900
Hmm.

02:33.100 --> 02:34.380
The teacher said he's doing good.

02:35.210 --> 02:37.620
The school has quotas for admission
to junior colleges every year.

02:38.380 --> 02:39.620
If he works harder

02:40.050 --> 02:40.930
on his cultural studies,

02:41.290 --> 02:41.770
it's possible for him.

02:44.260 --> 02:44.740
Let's hope so.

02:58.050 --> 02:58.850
Qiao Jinyu.

02:59.410 --> 03:00.660
I want to find

03:00.660 --> 03:02.260
Qiao Beiyu's boyfriend
in Nanqiao Village

03:02.380 --> 03:03.980
and find out what he did to Beiyu.

03:04.290 --> 03:05.850
What do you want to do?

03:06.180 --> 03:07.050
You have to help me.

03:08.180 --> 03:10.820
Isn't that a bad idea? How can I help?

03:11.050 --> 03:12.900
Mom won't spare me if she finds out.

03:13.020 --> 03:14.290
You have to listen to me.

03:14.290 --> 03:15.180
Why should I?

03:15.460 --> 03:16.690
Because I'm your sister

03:18.100 --> 03:21.050
and Qiao Beiyu is our elder sister.

03:23.020 --> 03:23.740
Don't worry.

03:23.740 --> 03:25.820
Even if something happens,
I won't drag you down.

03:27.050 --> 03:29.260
Why do I feel like

03:29.260 --> 03:31.780
you've changed?

03:34.150 --> 03:38.630
[Episode 5]
[Nanqiao's Secret Beau]

03:55.340 --> 03:56.410
Clean it up.

03:58.170 --> 03:58.820
No.

03:59.260 --> 04:00.610
Did anyone see that I did it?

04:01.170 --> 04:01.690
Qiao Qingyu.

04:01.980 --> 04:04.010
I advise you not to yell at us.

04:04.380 --> 04:05.660
Sheng is my best friend.

04:05.980 --> 04:07.450
Messing with me
is equivalent to messing with Sheng.

04:13.010 --> 04:14.170
What are you doing?

04:15.540 --> 04:16.170
Qiao Qingyu.

04:17.380 --> 04:18.060
Qiao Qingyu.

04:18.290 --> 04:18.980
What are you doing?

04:20.570 --> 04:22.290
See what Sheng will do to you.

04:28.500 --> 04:29.780
What's wrong?

04:30.820 --> 04:31.410
Nothing.

04:34.220 --> 04:35.780
Actually, something's going on.

04:36.659 --> 04:39.170
I put rubbish in Ming Sheng's schoolbag,

04:39.820 --> 04:41.659
but they bullied me first.

04:42.820 --> 04:44.980
Ming Sheng won't let me off.

04:45.380 --> 04:47.010
I'm not afraid of his revenge.

04:47.010 --> 04:48.570
I've been prepared for a long time.

04:49.500 --> 04:51.570
But I'm just a little nervous.

04:52.260 --> 04:53.820
Am I a little cowardly?

04:54.780 --> 04:56.820
You have such a rich imagination.

04:57.170 --> 04:59.060
Sheng isn't the person you think he is.

04:59.780 --> 05:01.010
Do you know Ming Sheng too?

05:01.410 --> 05:02.450
We're more than just acquaintances.

05:02.500 --> 05:04.850
We're neighbors,
and we grew up together.

05:06.570 --> 05:07.410
Let me tell you.

05:08.100 --> 05:10.220
He used my favorite dress as a child

05:10.220 --> 05:11.450
to make a cat bed.

05:12.010 --> 05:13.060
Sheng lost his first tooth

05:13.060 --> 05:15.010
in a fight with me.

05:15.690 --> 05:16.980
Sheng is playful,

05:17.010 --> 05:18.260
but he has a strong sense of justice

05:18.380 --> 05:19.380
and values loyalty.

05:21.170 --> 05:23.450
Don't be fooled
by his usual serious look.

05:23.660 --> 05:25.570
He's actually very kind

05:26.010 --> 05:27.220
and compassionate.

05:28.610 --> 05:29.610
Sometimes,

05:30.290 --> 05:31.820
he can be quite childish too.

05:37.570 --> 05:38.380
Gather round.

05:38.820 --> 05:40.460
Previously we learned the leg exercises

05:40.460 --> 05:42.220
for breaststroke on land.

05:42.490 --> 05:43.980
Let's practice underwater today.

05:44.290 --> 05:45.780
Stand in three rows.

05:46.409 --> 05:48.050
Once you hear the whistle, go.

05:49.020 --> 05:49.810
First row.

06:09.490 --> 06:10.660
Keep your legs straight.

06:17.370 --> 06:18.170
Qiao Qingyu!

06:18.780 --> 06:19.610
Focus.

06:25.580 --> 06:26.410
Keep your legs straight.

06:38.170 --> 06:39.460
Make sure it's clean.

06:39.460 --> 06:41.659
It's mostly just dust.

06:42.170 --> 06:43.050
They wipe off easily.

06:43.170 --> 06:45.020
Should I thank you

06:45.290 --> 06:46.490
for only dumping dust

06:46.490 --> 06:47.409
into Qiao Qingyu's bag?

06:47.980 --> 06:48.850
That's not necessary.

06:51.700 --> 06:53.659
You were taking this joke
a little too far.

06:54.100 --> 06:55.340
Wiping a schoolbag is nothing serious.

06:55.930 --> 06:56.980
Don't bully Qiao Qingyu.

06:57.659 --> 06:59.340
You spread the news

06:59.490 --> 07:00.850
about Qiao Beiyu

07:00.850 --> 07:02.250
and made Qiao Qingyu misunderstand me.

07:02.250 --> 07:03.780
I even took the blame for you.

07:04.490 --> 07:05.660
How should we settle this score?

07:06.700 --> 07:07.580
I heard about Qiao Beiyu

07:07.580 --> 07:09.980
from students from other schools

07:09.980 --> 07:10.850
and accidentally

07:10.850 --> 07:13.490
spread it among those at our school.

07:13.780 --> 07:14.490
I didn't expect her

07:14.490 --> 07:16.050
to think it was you.

07:33.170 --> 07:35.930
Sheng, are you serious?

07:36.370 --> 07:38.460
This will ruin my image

07:38.460 --> 07:38.810
as the school's heartthrob.

07:38.980 --> 07:41.250
Cut the nonsense and say your lines.

07:42.850 --> 07:43.980
It's all my fault.

07:44.580 --> 07:46.170
I'll take the blame.

07:46.900 --> 07:48.170
It's all my fault.

07:48.610 --> 07:50.170
I'll take the blame.

07:50.850 --> 07:52.020
It's all my fault.

07:52.409 --> 07:53.900
I'll take the blame.

07:53.900 --> 07:55.020
Is that enough?

07:56.580 --> 07:57.900
I'll spare you.

07:57.900 --> 07:58.900
Thank you, sir.

08:00.610 --> 08:03.100
I'll give you a sincere apology.

08:04.370 --> 08:05.050
Keep it for yourself.

08:05.050 --> 08:05.810
I'll give you a sincere apology.

08:05.810 --> 08:06.700
Keep it for yourself.

08:06.700 --> 08:07.490
Remember to return this wok

08:07.490 --> 08:08.850
to the shopkeeper.

08:09.730 --> 08:10.850
You'll have to clean it too.

08:10.850 --> 08:11.250
Alright.

08:41.419 --> 08:43.210
Sheng is playful,

08:43.780 --> 08:45.580
but he has a strong sense of justice

08:45.580 --> 08:46.580
and values loyalty.

08:46.580 --> 08:47.810
It's all my fault.

08:48.170 --> 08:49.610
I'll take the blame.

08:50.810 --> 08:52.810
Throw this for me. You're on duty today.

08:53.050 --> 08:55.370
Don't be fooled
by his usual serious look.

08:55.580 --> 08:57.410
He's actually very kind

08:57.850 --> 08:59.100
and compassionate.

09:02.700 --> 09:04.020
Borrow a uniform.

09:04.580 --> 09:05.460
Don't catch a cold.

09:32.980 --> 09:34.540
After deducting costs, the restaurant

09:35.410 --> 09:37.460
made just over 5,000 yuan this month.

09:37.900 --> 09:39.540
And deducting the rent, utilities,

09:39.540 --> 09:41.610
and the kids' expenses,

09:42.170 --> 09:43.900
we have less than 1,200 yuan.

09:44.810 --> 09:45.780
I think

09:47.170 --> 09:49.220
we should send Haisheng some money.

09:49.250 --> 09:51.490
Isn't he planning to fix the old house?

09:52.460 --> 09:54.290
Why don't you talk to him

09:54.810 --> 09:56.180
and see if he can help cover it for us?

09:56.180 --> 09:57.300
We'll pay him back next spring.

09:57.770 --> 09:59.180
That's inappropriate.

09:59.890 --> 10:01.610
You didn't answer
Wang's phone call, right?

10:03.010 --> 10:04.420
He called me.

10:04.650 --> 10:05.890
His son is getting married.

10:06.250 --> 10:07.980
We're long overdue.

10:08.010 --> 10:09.300
It's about time to pay him back.

10:09.370 --> 10:11.370
I've paid him the remaining 3,000 yuan.

10:17.060 --> 10:19.300
No, look.

10:20.180 --> 10:21.370
We three sons are responsible

10:21.370 --> 10:23.180
for repairing the house for our parents.

10:23.890 --> 10:25.180
With my second brother's
current condition,

10:25.180 --> 10:26.490
we can't count on him.

10:27.060 --> 10:28.700
So I think...

10:28.700 --> 10:29.610
What do you think we should do?

10:30.010 --> 10:31.530
Let's give him the 1,200 yuan

10:31.530 --> 10:32.220
on our account.

10:32.220 --> 10:33.580
How about we starve ourselves?

10:33.580 --> 10:34.820
That's not what I meant.

10:34.820 --> 10:35.460
I mean...

10:36.010 --> 10:38.060
I mean we should give him some money.

10:38.060 --> 10:39.100
All these years,

10:39.100 --> 10:40.980
Haisheng has been taking care of Dad.

10:40.980 --> 10:42.610
If you let him
pay for the house repairs alone,

10:44.370 --> 10:46.420
he'll bring up
what happened back then again.

10:46.700 --> 10:47.650
What's wrong with back then?

10:48.580 --> 10:50.420
Did we deserve to be bullied back then?

10:51.060 --> 10:52.010
They're good people,

10:52.010 --> 10:53.060
and we're not.

10:53.060 --> 10:53.820
We deserve

10:54.010 --> 10:55.460
their judgment, huh?

10:55.700 --> 10:56.890
That's not what I meant.

10:56.890 --> 10:58.300
Why are you so anxious?

10:58.300 --> 10:59.370
Of course you're never anxious.

10:59.820 --> 11:00.340
When something happens,

11:00.340 --> 11:02.220
all you do is hiding.

11:08.650 --> 11:09.460
Lady boss!

11:09.980 --> 11:11.370
Hey, Mr. Chen.

11:12.820 --> 11:14.420
Do you want
the vegetables delivered tomorrow?

11:14.420 --> 11:15.370
Yes.

11:15.400 --> 11:16.010
Mr. Chen.

11:16.010 --> 11:16.770
You came just in time.

11:16.770 --> 11:18.370
I just wanted to discuss it with you.

11:18.650 --> 11:20.580
We're never picky
about the vegetables you deliver.

11:20.580 --> 11:22.610
Can you give us a discount?

11:22.610 --> 11:24.060
Sometimes I throw away 100 grams
out of 500.

11:24.060 --> 11:25.060
It really doesn't add up.

11:25.060 --> 11:26.370
Do you want it or not?

11:27.010 --> 11:27.820
Yes.

11:41.420 --> 11:43.420
Before the teacher arrives
for the morning study session,

11:43.420 --> 11:45.700
copy this poem.

12:14.980 --> 12:18.300
I went out to visit
a few relatives and friends.

12:19.130 --> 12:20.850
The third day was the same.

12:24.730 --> 12:27.900
♪You opened a window♪

12:30.950 --> 12:34.800
♪I saw hope outside the window♪

12:37.130 --> 12:41.000
♪You said something
I couldn't understand♪

12:42.950 --> 12:46.350
♪And I realized my desire♪

12:46.350 --> 12:47.100
[Outstanding Class]

12:49.050 --> 12:52.930
♪You lit up a lamp♪

12:55.600 --> 12:58.900
♪I saw the light♪

12:59.500 --> 13:01.000
[Blooming Youth]

13:01.000 --> 13:04.400
♪You slowly walked away♪

13:07.250 --> 13:10.550
♪And I realized my helplessness♪

13:24.300 --> 13:24.980
Well,

13:25.850 --> 13:27.370
I was going to throw these shoes away,

13:28.650 --> 13:29.650
but since someone

13:29.850 --> 13:31.370
made them so clean,

13:31.370 --> 13:32.490
I'll wear them

13:32.890 --> 13:34.010
for a few more days.

13:37.100 --> 13:39.180
Keep helping me with my homework
this semester.

13:39.370 --> 13:41.300
I'm taking the TEF,

13:41.700 --> 13:42.490
so I won't be free.

13:43.180 --> 13:44.460
But don't misunderstand.

13:44.700 --> 13:46.940
I'm not going to use my favor

13:47.180 --> 13:48.250
to help you get the medical records.

13:49.060 --> 13:50.890
After all, doing homework

13:51.100 --> 13:52.300
is much harder than this.

13:53.650 --> 13:55.370
I can help you with your homework,

13:55.610 --> 13:57.580
but I need two things in exchange.

13:58.650 --> 13:59.850
They're not difficult for you.

14:00.700 --> 14:01.490
Speak.

14:01.580 --> 14:03.890
First, let me borrow your phone
for a few days.

14:04.220 --> 14:04.820
Second,

14:04.940 --> 14:07.340
you found the letter, didn't you?
Give it back to me.

14:20.490 --> 14:22.610
You can have my phone.

14:26.180 --> 14:27.180
Where's the letter?

14:27.180 --> 14:29.730
I forgot to bring it.
I'll go home and find it.

14:33.420 --> 14:34.220
Studying hard

14:35.060 --> 14:36.180
is what matters the most.

14:55.580 --> 14:56.130
Sheng.

14:57.220 --> 14:57.650
Hey.

15:09.580 --> 15:10.820
There's something

15:10.890 --> 15:12.010
I can't figure out.

15:12.250 --> 15:13.370
Help me with it.

15:13.980 --> 15:14.770
What is it?

15:18.220 --> 15:19.890
I have a friend.

15:19.890 --> 15:20.820
A guy.

15:21.650 --> 15:22.460
He likes

15:22.460 --> 15:24.770
to hide other people's letters to girls.

15:25.100 --> 15:27.850
Don't you think
there's something wrong with him?

15:29.580 --> 15:32.010
He probably didn't hide anyone else's,

15:32.180 --> 15:33.580
except this girl's.

15:33.580 --> 15:34.250
Yes.

15:36.100 --> 15:37.610
There's nothing wrong with him.

15:37.820 --> 15:38.820
He likes her.

15:39.420 --> 15:40.220
Who likes who?

15:40.250 --> 15:42.700
The guy hiding the letter
likes the girl.

15:42.820 --> 15:43.770
Nonsense!

15:47.460 --> 15:48.770
What I'm trying to say

15:49.420 --> 15:51.300
is I know this guy and it's impossible.

15:53.220 --> 15:54.300
Sometimes

15:54.700 --> 15:56.130
pride makes

15:56.130 --> 15:58.220
people say things they don't mean.

15:58.220 --> 16:01.010
They deceive others and even themselves.

16:01.250 --> 16:02.700
Things always happen this way.

16:07.180 --> 16:08.180
With so much said,

16:08.370 --> 16:09.820
who's the guy?

16:12.650 --> 16:13.580
Nobody.

16:14.420 --> 16:15.180
It's from a TV show

16:15.180 --> 16:16.820
I watched yesterday.

16:18.610 --> 16:20.580
Since when
do you love watching TV shows?

16:26.820 --> 16:27.770
You're blushing.

16:27.770 --> 16:29.460
Me? Blushing?

16:33.490 --> 16:35.420
It's probably because
it's too hot today.

16:36.100 --> 16:38.420
It's normal.

16:39.250 --> 16:40.180
Oh, the sun is scorching.

16:52.060 --> 16:53.610
You've performed
so many surgeries today.

16:53.610 --> 16:54.700
Are you exhausted?

16:55.580 --> 16:56.370
Hmm.

16:57.770 --> 16:58.580
I'm exhausted.

17:02.420 --> 17:06.220
We had a patient in surgery today
with a history of Hepatitis B.

17:08.770 --> 17:10.300
There was an accident
when opening the artery.

17:10.700 --> 17:13.099
I accidentally got blood in my eye.

17:18.180 --> 17:19.980
I've read your medical report
from last month.

17:20.250 --> 17:21.980
Your anti-HBs is greater than 100.

17:22.060 --> 17:23.819
You also received
a Hepatitis B immunoglobulin injection.

17:24.010 --> 17:24.890
You should be fine.

17:25.460 --> 17:25.980
Don't worry.

17:40.180 --> 17:42.850
I heard that a new amusement park
has opened in the development zone.

17:43.980 --> 17:45.650
It happens to be our day off tomorrow.

17:46.220 --> 17:48.580
Shall we bring Sheng with us there

17:48.580 --> 17:49.420
to relax?

18:00.370 --> 18:01.580
Okay, got it.

18:02.180 --> 18:03.100
Notify them immediately.

18:07.610 --> 18:09.850
The organ donor
who was in a car accident

18:09.850 --> 18:11.610
suddenly fell into a deep coma

18:11.980 --> 18:13.460
and was initially diagnosed
as brain-dead.

18:13.890 --> 18:15.300
So a liver transplant

18:15.300 --> 18:17.220
must be performed immediately tonight.

18:19.770 --> 18:22.370
Dr. Li, immediately inform your team

18:22.610 --> 18:24.700
that the transplant of Tan Qianqian
in Room 2, Bed 6,

18:24.700 --> 18:25.980
has been moved to tonight.

18:26.370 --> 18:29.140
Yes, I'll expedite
the fast-track pathway approval now.

18:29.250 --> 18:30.700
Okay, thanks.

18:32.810 --> 18:34.290
Eat it.

18:34.460 --> 18:36.010
You've cured so many,

18:36.220 --> 18:38.220
but your chronic gastritis is worsening.

18:42.290 --> 18:43.090
Oh.

18:43.900 --> 18:44.700
Oh, right.

18:46.090 --> 18:48.420
Sheng's in full rebellion,

18:48.620 --> 18:49.810
making our relationship tense.

18:50.380 --> 18:51.460
I'm worried

18:51.460 --> 18:52.980
that if I make
our relationship public now,

18:53.250 --> 18:55.660
he'll be even more upset.

18:56.010 --> 18:56.980
So I'm thinking

18:57.730 --> 18:59.620
maybe we could wait
until he finishes his NCEE

18:59.810 --> 19:01.620
before revealing our relationship.

19:06.090 --> 19:07.620
He'll grow up

19:08.770 --> 19:10.090
and understand.

19:12.220 --> 19:13.570
I'll make arrangements for the surgery.

19:13.570 --> 19:14.620
Oh, okay.

19:43.900 --> 19:46.530
Mom, I was told
that there's something wrong

19:46.700 --> 19:49.050
with my student information.

19:49.220 --> 19:50.090
I need to bring

19:50.090 --> 19:51.810
my household registration book
to school to fix it.

19:51.810 --> 19:52.810
How careless.

19:52.980 --> 19:54.180
I'll get it for you in the morning.

19:54.810 --> 19:56.810
No, Mom. Get it for me now.

19:57.090 --> 19:59.620
What if I forget it tomorrow morning?

19:59.810 --> 20:01.980
My teacher's reminded me several times,

20:01.980 --> 20:03.490
but I've forgotten about it
for the past few days.

20:04.810 --> 20:06.620
Okay, I'll get it for you now.

20:07.900 --> 20:08.530
I don't know

20:08.530 --> 20:10.250
what's going on
in your head all day long.

20:41.010 --> 20:42.050
Ah!

20:43.220 --> 20:43.940
What's happened?

20:44.330 --> 20:45.050
What's wrong?

20:45.460 --> 20:45.980
Mom.

20:46.050 --> 20:46.570
Did you scald your hand?

20:46.620 --> 20:48.530
I'll take it myself, then.

20:48.530 --> 20:48.900
Gosh.

20:49.220 --> 20:51.460
You scalded your hand doing that? How?

20:52.220 --> 20:54.090
Hurry. You'll be alright
after rinsing it with cold water.

21:00.620 --> 21:01.660
What if it leaves a scar?

21:12.980 --> 21:14.220
How did it go? Did you get everything?

21:15.810 --> 21:16.220
Here.

21:18.220 --> 21:19.380
I was short on time.

21:19.460 --> 21:21.770
So I just snapped a few pictures
of what was in the drawer.

21:21.770 --> 21:22.980
Just bear with it.

21:28.460 --> 21:31.490
This is Beiyu's

21:31.490 --> 21:32.810
hospital bill.

21:33.050 --> 21:35.900
In total, it's around 150,000
to 160,000 yuan.

21:40.290 --> 21:42.980
Jinrui probably gave Mom the money.

21:43.180 --> 21:44.420
He pays her every month.

21:46.220 --> 21:47.700
Based on the timeline,

21:47.860 --> 21:49.900
he began paying Mom
as soon as he started working.

21:50.090 --> 21:51.810
Why did he give our family
so much money?

21:52.090 --> 21:54.250
Jinrui is nice to our family.

21:54.250 --> 21:55.940
We've spent over 100,000 yuan

21:56.050 --> 21:57.660
just on Beiyu's medical bills,

21:57.810 --> 21:59.090
and we're still in debt to other people.

21:59.220 --> 22:01.050
He must have seen our family's struggles

22:01.570 --> 22:03.180
and gave us

22:03.620 --> 22:05.420
some of his salary to help.

22:05.660 --> 22:07.010
He has always been nice to us.

22:07.010 --> 22:07.900
Everyone knows that.

22:10.900 --> 22:12.290
Is that all?

22:15.220 --> 22:16.220
Mom didn't take long

22:16.220 --> 22:18.220
to apply medicine to you.

22:18.660 --> 22:20.700
I even almost got caught.

22:25.980 --> 22:28.620
Qingyu, I don't get it.

22:28.620 --> 22:30.290
You were so desperate

22:30.290 --> 22:32.140
to find out
the cause of Qiao Beiyu's death.

22:32.330 --> 22:34.660
Hasn't everything been investigated?

22:34.980 --> 22:36.380
Qiao Beiyu died mysteriously.

22:36.380 --> 22:38.490
Come on, she died of illness,

22:38.620 --> 22:40.420
not murder.

22:40.490 --> 22:43.180
Are we going to find a murderer?

22:43.250 --> 22:45.090
Even if she made a bad choice

22:45.420 --> 22:46.980
in boyfriends,

22:47.420 --> 22:48.810
she's gone now.

22:48.810 --> 22:50.770
Let's not bring up old issues.

22:50.810 --> 22:52.050
Like what Mom said,

22:52.620 --> 22:54.700
everyone will forget in the end.

22:57.620 --> 22:58.420
We have a deal.

22:59.460 --> 23:01.380
This is all I can do to help you.

23:01.380 --> 23:03.420
I don't want to get involved
in this mess again.

23:04.220 --> 23:05.290
If Mom finds out,

23:05.290 --> 23:07.900
both of us will be done for.

24:14.770 --> 24:15.570
Qiao Beiyu.

24:18.900 --> 24:19.770
Qiao Beiyu.

24:20.620 --> 24:21.460
Qiao Beiyu.

24:24.250 --> 24:25.620
Qiao Beiyu, is it you?

24:40.090 --> 24:40.900
Qiao Beiyu.

24:41.700 --> 24:43.220
Even if it's just me,

24:43.250 --> 24:45.180
I will find out the truth for you.

24:45.570 --> 24:47.290
It's not only for those still alive,

24:49.220 --> 24:50.250
but also for you.

25:16.620 --> 25:19.460
Mom, I was told
that there's something wrong

25:19.460 --> 25:21.700
with my student information.

25:21.860 --> 25:23.380
I need to bring

25:23.380 --> 25:24.460
my household registration book
to school to fix it.

25:25.050 --> 25:27.460
Mom, I'll take it myself, then.

25:32.290 --> 25:33.180
How dare you steal?

25:33.770 --> 25:34.660
Who taught you to do it?

25:35.290 --> 25:36.290
Explain.

25:39.090 --> 25:39.900
Qiao Qingyu.

25:40.980 --> 25:41.770
Come in.

25:50.620 --> 25:52.010
Your brother has come clean
about everything.

25:52.220 --> 25:52.900
This money

25:53.570 --> 25:54.980
was taken from my drawer.

25:55.250 --> 25:56.460
What's with this phone?

25:56.460 --> 25:57.180
Where is it from?

25:58.770 --> 25:59.460
I found it.

25:59.460 --> 26:00.220
Where was it?

26:01.180 --> 26:03.220
I found it
in the school library last week.

26:04.980 --> 26:06.010
You found it
in the school library last week,

26:06.010 --> 26:06.860
and it's still with you.

26:06.860 --> 26:08.010
That's called stealing.
Don't you know that?

26:08.620 --> 26:10.180
Ask her anything you like,
but don't hit her.

26:10.180 --> 26:11.620
How could you defend her?

26:11.860 --> 26:12.810
If I don't discipline her,

26:12.810 --> 26:14.090
she'll end up in the police station.

26:14.980 --> 26:16.010
I'm asking you one last time.

26:16.860 --> 26:18.770
Where did you get this phone?

26:19.010 --> 26:20.290
Did you buy it?

26:20.290 --> 26:21.220
How much did you spend on it?

26:21.220 --> 26:22.380
Or did someone give it to you?

26:22.490 --> 26:23.570
What's going on?

26:24.420 --> 26:26.010
I found it at school.

26:27.220 --> 26:28.460
You found it at school?

26:29.180 --> 26:30.980
Okay, I'm not going to the shop today.

26:30.980 --> 26:32.940
I'm going to school with you.

26:33.180 --> 26:34.980
We'll find out when we get to school.

26:35.010 --> 26:36.220
Enough, you...

26:38.900 --> 26:40.050
Is finding a phone that easy?

26:40.050 --> 26:41.980
You can't even make up a lie.

26:45.490 --> 26:46.770
Hurry!

26:49.490 --> 26:50.900
Explain to your mom.

26:51.220 --> 26:52.810
Your brother doesn't
think things through.

26:53.420 --> 26:54.810
He rummaged through the drawer
this time.

26:54.810 --> 26:56.460
Who knows what he'll do next?

26:57.380 --> 26:58.250
I can't believe

26:58.860 --> 27:00.490
you told him to do such horrible things.

27:00.810 --> 27:02.180
I did tell him
to look through the drawer,

27:02.180 --> 27:03.420
but I didn't tell him
to steal the money.

27:05.380 --> 27:07.620
I just want to know how Qiao Beiyu died

27:07.810 --> 27:08.420
and...

27:08.660 --> 27:09.490
And what?

27:09.570 --> 27:10.980
And who killed her.

27:10.980 --> 27:11.980
No one killed her.

27:16.180 --> 27:16.980
Mom.

27:20.900 --> 27:22.570
I found this back home.

27:31.420 --> 27:32.220
Where is it from?

27:32.460 --> 27:33.010
The old house was on fire.

27:33.010 --> 27:34.810
It was found in Aunt Qin's drawer.

27:35.220 --> 27:36.490
Everything else was burned.

27:36.490 --> 27:37.660
These are the only ones left.

27:48.980 --> 27:51.330
Mom, is everything written

27:51.330 --> 27:52.460
in Qiao Beiyu's diary true?

27:58.980 --> 28:00.770
What does it matter if it's true or not?

28:02.010 --> 28:03.290
The dead can't be brought back to life.

28:05.700 --> 28:08.010
I didn't want
to talk to her much back then,

28:08.220 --> 28:09.490
but I understand her now.

28:10.420 --> 28:12.050
The rumors about her are horrible.

28:12.050 --> 28:13.620
I shouldn't have listened
to their nonsense,

28:13.660 --> 28:15.180
but I was afraid to ask you.

28:15.180 --> 28:16.050
I looked through the drawer

28:16.050 --> 28:17.900
to find out what happened.

28:17.900 --> 28:19.250
No matter what happened to her,

28:20.420 --> 28:22.380
she shouldn't have disrespected herself.

28:25.220 --> 28:27.620
I've grown up.

28:27.620 --> 28:28.700
You can tell me

28:28.700 --> 28:29.460
what's going on at home.

28:29.460 --> 28:30.810
I can share the burden.

28:32.770 --> 28:34.050
Qiao Beiyu didn't die of appendicitis.

28:34.050 --> 28:35.660
Her boyfriend from Nanqiao Village
is the culprit,

28:35.660 --> 28:36.220
isn't he?

28:37.620 --> 28:38.380
Qiao Qingyu.

28:40.620 --> 28:43.290
Qiao Beiyu died
of complications from appendicitis.

28:44.220 --> 28:46.220
Where did you hear this nonsense?

28:46.220 --> 28:47.380
The diagnosis from People's Hospital

28:47.380 --> 28:47.980
says AIDS.

28:47.980 --> 28:49.050
I know that.

28:49.050 --> 28:50.420
You're all grown-up now, aren't you?

28:54.290 --> 28:55.140
Qiao Qingyu, let me tell you.

28:55.620 --> 28:57.420
I'll let you know what you need to know.

28:57.460 --> 28:58.460
Don't worry

28:58.460 --> 28:59.620
about the rest.

29:00.980 --> 29:02.380
Just mind your own business.

29:02.770 --> 29:04.460
Look at what you've become!

29:05.810 --> 29:06.980
You led your brother astray

29:06.980 --> 29:07.900
and spied on me.

29:08.530 --> 29:09.810
And the phone.

29:09.980 --> 29:10.810
How could you just

29:10.810 --> 29:11.980
happen to find a new phone?

29:11.980 --> 29:13.460
You even kept it for a few days.

29:13.460 --> 29:14.290
What's going on?

29:18.620 --> 29:20.490
Fine, you're not coming clean, are you?

29:20.980 --> 29:23.010
I'll find out when we get to school.

29:23.220 --> 29:24.810
Qiao Qingyu, I'm your mom.

29:24.810 --> 29:26.620
I'll always be responsible for you.

29:42.380 --> 29:44.620
Qingyu, I've talked to your mother.

29:45.010 --> 29:45.980
Just tell the truth,

29:45.980 --> 29:47.290
and we'll drop it.

29:47.620 --> 29:49.010
I won't ask you

29:49.050 --> 29:49.980
where you got this phone.

29:53.050 --> 29:53.860
Your teacher won't harm you.

29:53.860 --> 29:55.090
So, say something.

29:55.660 --> 29:58.010
Qingyu, no one's here right now.

29:58.180 --> 29:59.620
If you didn't get it legitimately,

29:59.660 --> 30:00.770
telling the truth

30:01.050 --> 30:02.660
gives you a way out

30:02.770 --> 30:03.620
and a second chance.

30:03.700 --> 30:04.860
If you got it legitimately,

30:04.860 --> 30:06.050
coming clean

30:06.460 --> 30:07.700
will clear your name.

30:08.700 --> 30:10.010
I found this phone

30:10.010 --> 30:11.380
in the library last week.

30:14.420 --> 30:15.570
If you found it last week,

30:15.570 --> 30:16.420
why haven't you given

30:16.420 --> 30:17.660
it to your teacher?

30:17.700 --> 30:19.250
That sounds a lot like stealing,
doesn't it?

30:19.700 --> 30:21.180
Believe it or not,

30:21.180 --> 30:22.770
I wouldn't do such a thing.

30:23.420 --> 30:24.860
I will return this phone.

30:27.420 --> 30:28.980
Did you see Sun call Qiao Qingyu

30:28.980 --> 30:30.380
into his office?

30:30.530 --> 30:30.940
What?

30:31.220 --> 30:32.490
I heard she stole something.

30:34.730 --> 30:36.380
Once they've investigated everything,

30:36.730 --> 30:37.980
she can't escape punishment.

30:38.180 --> 30:39.530
Maybe she'll get expelled.

30:40.490 --> 30:42.140
Good afternoon, students.

30:42.420 --> 30:45.140
Here's a lost-and-found announcement.

30:45.380 --> 30:46.460
Last Friday,

30:46.460 --> 30:49.660
a student found a Nokia N95 phone

30:49.660 --> 30:52.490
in the school library's reading room.

30:53.090 --> 30:55.770
If you lost your phone,

30:55.770 --> 30:57.050
please come to the radio station
immediately.

30:57.290 --> 30:58.570
Your teacher said

30:58.940 --> 30:59.700
you were always a loner

30:59.700 --> 31:01.220
at school.

31:02.490 --> 31:03.290
That's not quite appropriate.

31:06.730 --> 31:08.620
We're from a small town.

31:09.730 --> 31:10.900
We can't compare

31:11.050 --> 31:12.700
with your classmates in every aspect.

31:13.180 --> 31:14.330
You know

31:15.420 --> 31:16.620
your father and I
aren't very successful.

31:17.140 --> 31:18.330
We run a small noodle shop,

31:18.900 --> 31:20.940
and despite working hard every day,
we don't earn much.

31:21.290 --> 31:22.770
We can't afford
to buy you anything good.

31:24.900 --> 31:27.330
But the more it is like this,
the more you need to rely on yourself.

31:28.900 --> 31:30.090
Do your best to improve yourself.

31:31.530 --> 31:33.380
Work harder on your studies.

31:34.380 --> 31:35.660
This way, you won't feel inferior,

31:36.530 --> 31:38.090
no matter where you go.

31:41.700 --> 31:42.770
I don't want you

31:43.220 --> 31:44.900
to end up like me.

31:48.140 --> 31:49.220
At this age,

31:52.140 --> 31:54.420
girls need to start living
for themselves.

31:55.700 --> 31:57.140
Be careful,

31:57.730 --> 31:59.180
because one wrong step
can trigger a cascade of errors.

32:01.090 --> 32:03.490
I heard
the owner of that phone was found.

32:03.860 --> 32:05.900
It's an N95 and it's been days.

32:05.900 --> 32:07.530
The owner is so careless.

32:07.530 --> 32:08.490
Who knows?

32:08.900 --> 32:09.900
Come on. Let's go to the cafeteria.

32:15.810 --> 32:17.140
A scar would be ugly and obvious.

32:18.490 --> 32:20.330
You should cherish yourself the most.

32:20.940 --> 32:22.770
Listen to me. I won't hurt you.

32:30.140 --> 32:31.980
Why did you come back
wearing a pair of boys' shoes?

32:41.900 --> 32:42.700
Sheng!

32:46.900 --> 32:47.700
Didn't you want to play basketball?

32:48.090 --> 32:48.900
Why did you leave alone first?

32:49.050 --> 32:49.460
Something came up.

32:49.810 --> 32:50.290
You abandoned your teammates,
didn't you?

32:50.730 --> 32:51.140
No.

32:52.530 --> 32:54.180
This pair of shoes is quite popular.

32:54.330 --> 32:54.730
Bubble tea, then.

33:06.530 --> 33:08.900
Madam, we found the owner.

33:11.220 --> 33:13.420
This is Wang Mumu from Class 1, Grade 3.

33:13.770 --> 33:16.420
The phone Qiao Qingyu found was hers.

33:16.700 --> 33:17.490
Hello, madam.

33:17.700 --> 33:19.460
I left my phone on a shelf

33:19.460 --> 33:20.570
in the library.

33:20.700 --> 33:21.730
Glad you found it.

33:22.220 --> 33:23.980
My phone is a Nokia N95

33:24.010 --> 33:25.980
with a silver front and a black back.

33:25.980 --> 33:27.980
There are also two scratches
on the back. One deep and one shallow.

33:28.220 --> 33:29.730
I accidentally dropped it on the ground

33:29.730 --> 33:31.490
while taking the bus.

33:31.490 --> 33:33.090
You can check if you don't believe me.

33:34.330 --> 33:35.700
No need. All that matters is it's yours.

33:36.810 --> 33:38.620
Mumu told me

33:38.900 --> 33:40.770
that she lost her phone accidentally,

33:41.140 --> 33:43.290
so this matter is settled.

33:49.330 --> 33:50.380
Wang Mumu.

33:52.660 --> 33:53.860
Thank you for earlier.

33:56.770 --> 33:59.290
Is that all?

34:00.380 --> 34:01.330
What do you want, then?

34:01.330 --> 34:03.290
I don't have much allowance.

34:04.570 --> 34:05.570
Qiao Qingyu.

34:05.570 --> 34:07.860
You're cute when you're serious.

34:08.330 --> 34:09.900
No wonder he likes to bully you.

34:12.900 --> 34:14.139
I'm just doing him a favor.

34:14.460 --> 34:15.980
You can thank him

34:16.179 --> 34:17.090
if you really want to.

34:26.530 --> 34:28.420
Those fools from Class 2

34:28.900 --> 34:29.900
challenged us to a three-on-three.

34:29.900 --> 34:31.179
Aren't they just asking for trouble?

34:31.659 --> 34:32.179
Sheng.

34:32.730 --> 34:34.620
That three-pointer of yours was awesome.

34:35.420 --> 34:36.139
So sweaty.

34:37.659 --> 34:38.570
Those girls were so loud.

34:39.489 --> 34:40.980
They nearly blew my eardrums out.

34:41.570 --> 34:44.489
Yeah, I think I'm pretty cool
when playing basketball.

34:44.860 --> 34:45.860
Why don't I have any fans?

34:51.480 --> 34:52.429
[Thank You]

34:53.570 --> 34:54.330
"Thank you."

34:56.050 --> 34:58.140
Seriously, who is so miserly
that they'd thank someone

34:58.420 --> 34:59.570
with just a bottle of water?

35:00.140 --> 35:01.420
But the writing is quite good.

35:02.700 --> 35:04.490
Was it given to you by an admirer?

35:07.140 --> 35:08.250
Maybe.

35:09.570 --> 35:10.490
Maybe?

35:37.980 --> 35:39.690
Can you lower it down?

35:39.690 --> 35:40.610
So annoying.

35:42.170 --> 35:43.860
What does it have to do with me?
It was Mom.

35:44.210 --> 35:45.090
Did Mom go out?

35:45.340 --> 35:47.010
Yeah, she went out with a brazier.

36:34.050 --> 36:35.940
At 6:05 PM on the 24th,

36:36.050 --> 36:38.260
our country successfully launched
the Chang'e-1 satellite into space

36:38.300 --> 36:40.740
[Qiao's Handmade Noodle House]
using the Long March 3A rocket

36:40.740 --> 36:43.380
from Xichang Satellite Launch Center.

36:43.650 --> 36:46.050
The Chang'e-1 satellite marked
our country's

36:46.050 --> 36:47.780
first independently developed
lunar exploration mission.

36:48.130 --> 36:49.300
Its successful launch

36:49.300 --> 36:51.490
marks an important step
in the implementation...

36:51.940 --> 36:52.420
Qing.

36:52.420 --> 36:53.170
...of the Chinese lunar probe project.

36:53.170 --> 36:53.820
It's almost time.

36:53.820 --> 36:54.860
Go home to do your homework.

36:54.860 --> 36:55.610
Hmm.

36:56.650 --> 36:58.530
Dad, I have to go home
and do my homework too.

36:58.690 --> 36:59.460
What homework?

36:59.460 --> 37:00.530
You just want to go home
and play video games.

37:04.050 --> 37:05.260
Hello, sit anywhere you like.

37:11.010 --> 37:11.940
Table two's noodles are ready.

37:12.490 --> 37:13.300
Coming.

37:14.340 --> 37:15.380
You must be Qingyu.

37:18.530 --> 37:19.570
Who are you?

37:19.860 --> 37:21.050
How do you know my sister's name?

37:21.690 --> 37:24.460
The son of Mr. He from Nanqiao Village?

37:25.740 --> 37:26.530
He...

37:26.940 --> 37:28.690
Ms. Li, my name is He Feihai.

37:36.900 --> 37:38.010
I didn't expect you

37:38.010 --> 37:39.170
to come over today.

37:40.420 --> 37:41.820
I attended university in Huanzhou

37:42.340 --> 37:43.260
and just graduated recently.

37:43.690 --> 37:44.260
Thank you, Ms. Li.

37:45.010 --> 37:46.980
Mr. Qiao, I heard from Jinrui

37:47.300 --> 37:48.780
that you opened
a noodle house in Huanzhou.

37:49.260 --> 37:50.650
That's why I came by today.

37:51.380 --> 37:52.170
Thank you.

37:53.090 --> 37:54.610
How are your parents doing?

37:54.820 --> 37:55.490
They're quite good.

37:57.050 --> 37:58.490
Your parents are lucky.

37:58.980 --> 38:00.010
Raising a university student

38:00.570 --> 38:02.380
is worthwhile, however challenging.

38:03.090 --> 38:04.940
I'm no match for Jinrui.

38:08.130 --> 38:09.300
Mr. Qiao, Ms. Li.

38:09.650 --> 38:10.780
I also came here today

38:11.690 --> 38:12.650
because...

38:14.090 --> 38:15.210
You might not know

38:16.170 --> 38:18.490
that Beiyu and I were classmates.

38:18.530 --> 38:20.690
I heard about what happened to her
not long ago.

38:21.690 --> 38:23.300
I'm sorry for your loss.

38:23.300 --> 38:26.380
Let's not bring up the past.

38:28.130 --> 38:29.900
Well... Help yourself.

38:29.900 --> 38:31.650
I cooked a few dishes today,

38:31.650 --> 38:34.490
but I followed
the recipes from our hometown.

38:34.650 --> 38:35.740
You can't get them anywhere else.

38:36.530 --> 38:37.650
I remember now.

38:38.260 --> 38:41.130
He Feihai was Jinrui's follower.

38:41.380 --> 38:43.260
He always followed Beiyu and Jinrui

38:43.260 --> 38:43.940
around.

38:45.640 --> 38:47.640
Qiao Beiyu wrote in her diary

38:47.800 --> 38:49.560
that her favorite person
had come to Huanzhou.

38:49.920 --> 38:52.000
He Feihai went to university
in Huanzhou.

38:52.800 --> 38:54.120
Could he be Qiao Beiyu's boyfriend

38:54.120 --> 38:55.320
from Nanqiao Village?

38:58.680 --> 39:01.800
You're not looking
for trouble again, are you?

39:02.280 --> 39:05.440
I don't want to go through
Mom's wrath again.

39:06.320 --> 39:08.360
Don't worry. I'll take
full responsibility for what I do.

39:09.560 --> 39:11.280
Go get a bowl of rice. Hurry.

39:30.000 --> 39:35.200
[Meet me Monday at 6:30 PM at the cafe
by Huanzhou High School.]

39:36.160 --> 39:37.200
Come on. I'll walk you.

39:37.720 --> 39:38.720
[Qiao's Handmade Noodle House]
No need, Mr. Qiao.

39:39.320 --> 39:40.400
Your dad and I

39:40.560 --> 39:42.080
grew up together,

39:42.440 --> 39:43.800
so you don't have to be so formal.

39:44.080 --> 39:45.840
If you have any cravings,
just come over.

39:46.320 --> 39:47.680
Sure, thank you.

39:48.200 --> 39:51.320
Feihai, we made some pickled vegetables.

39:51.320 --> 39:52.240
Take it home.

39:52.600 --> 39:54.560
You're too generous.

39:54.560 --> 39:55.880
Fanghao made it herself. Just take it.

39:57.840 --> 39:58.520
Sure.

39:58.960 --> 40:01.400
Thank you, Qingyu. Thank you, Ms. Li.

40:01.680 --> 40:02.640
I'll head back now.

40:03.080 --> 40:04.080
I'll visit you another day.

40:05.360 --> 40:05.960
Take care.

40:23.960 --> 40:25.240
He was the champion last year.

40:26.440 --> 40:26.960
Let me see.

40:26.960 --> 40:27.840
Why are you here?

40:27.960 --> 40:28.840
We signed up.

40:29.000 --> 40:29.680
You signed up?

40:29.880 --> 40:30.320
Yeah.

40:30.760 --> 40:31.800
The four of us could make a team.

40:31.800 --> 40:32.720
No, we're not playing.

40:33.040 --> 40:34.200
There's a basketball game at school

40:34.200 --> 40:35.480
after school today.

40:35.760 --> 40:36.720
As the host,

40:37.000 --> 40:38.840
we should all be there to cheer

40:38.960 --> 40:40.040
for our classmates.

40:40.200 --> 40:41.360
Okay!

40:43.520 --> 40:44.960
Qingyu, are you going
to the basketball game?

40:45.120 --> 40:45.880
No.

40:47.960 --> 40:49.360
Qiao Qingyu doesn't think of herself

40:49.360 --> 40:51.200
as a member of us.

40:51.560 --> 40:52.400
Indeed.

40:53.400 --> 40:54.760
Come on. The game's about to start.

40:55.280 --> 40:56.160
Let's go.

41:10.300 --> 41:11.460
Help me get the menu.

41:13.780 --> 41:14.460
This is the menu.

41:14.460 --> 41:15.940
See if you like something to drink.

41:18.260 --> 41:19.530
You asked me out today

41:20.340 --> 41:22.050
to ask about Beiyu, didn't you?

41:56.280 --> 41:59.970
♪Perhaps♪

42:00.480 --> 42:06.180
♪The more we care,
the more careful we become♪

42:07.320 --> 42:12.720
♪Counting the distance
that separates us♪

42:13.720 --> 42:19.280
♪A single step,
and we'd be closer still♪

42:24.950 --> 42:28.620
♪In the future♪

42:29.080 --> 42:34.800
♪Time will reveal this secret♪

42:36.300 --> 42:41.370
♪Waiting is a silent promise♪

42:42.620 --> 42:47.780
♪That never expires♪

42:51.380 --> 42:55.850
♪Turns out that what's on my mind♪

42:56.850 --> 43:00.520
♪Is your name♪

43:01.020 --> 43:06.120
♪The only stubbornness in my heart♪

43:07.200 --> 43:10.420
♪At first sight♪

43:10.850 --> 43:14.130
♪The future has been determined♪

43:14.820 --> 43:20.380
♪Dreams began to feel real♪

43:21.480 --> 43:25.020
♪Turns out that what's on your mind♪

43:25.480 --> 43:29.420
♪Is a place♪

43:29.720 --> 43:35.280
♪Where the same story is held dear♪

43:35.950 --> 43:39.320
♪Fortunately, I'm not sensible enough♪

43:39.650 --> 43:43.120
♪Courage wasn't late too♪

43:43.650 --> 43:49.720
♪Only then does time not betray
our acquaintance♪
